item.title:
Andrew Garfield and Daisy Edgar-Jones to star in Sebastián Lelio’s ‘VOYAGERS.’
The film is set in 1977 as NASA prepared to launch humanity’s first interstellar probes. But what starts out as a mission becomes an epic, unexpected love story between Carl Sagan and Ann Druyan.
